{"tid":91824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【巴馬火腿真相】重病受傷滿身屎 意國農場地獄 擠迫互踩豬吃豬","createTime":"2017-01-23T06:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T10:40:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"505a47e42bd9b21b7b96e974ef6e1c9cfb240412","tid":91824,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170123/56206455 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170123%2F56206455%20&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=bc708032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170123%2F56206455%20&h=6512678f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170123/56206455 </a><br />\n<br />\n意大利巴馬火腿（Parma ham）非常出名，售價高昂，但有動物組織揭發，供應豬隻製作巴馬火腿的意大利養豬場以極不人道方法養豬，豬欄衞生環境惡劣，幾乎每隻都受傷或生病而且遭到虐打，有組織成員形容養豬場形同地獄。 <br />\n<br />\n意大利保護動物組織「Essere Animali」在意大利北部的艾米利亞羅馬涅（Emilia Romagna）一個養豬場安裝隱閉攝錄機，監察豬場情況長達6個月，他們發現這個養豬場有6座建築物飼養了6,000隻豬。 <br />\n<br />\n豬隻不見天日地擠在狹窄擠迫的豬欄內，地上身上佈滿排洩物，由於空間太少，牠們走動時會互相踐踏，較弱的豬就被踏在蹄下；牠們多數都受傷或生病，有豬隻因為無法取得食物，甚至吃同類，一些豬只剩半隻耳朵，也有一些豬尾巴被咬去。 <br />\n<br />\n片段中一隻瘦弱的豬在走廊上被農場工人猛推，亦有工人趕豬去屠宰時揮動木棍虐打和踢牠們。 <br />\n<br />\n負責調查的動物組織成員安德烈亞（Andrea）形容豬場如煉獄，他說：「幾乎所有豬隻都是骯髒和受傷的，大部份都是耳朵和尾部（受傷），另一些豬進食時感到被壓迫和沮喪，有些豬快要死了，不能活動，發出脆弱的聲音。」 <br />\n<br />\n雖然監控生產巴馬火腿的財團強調只是個別事件，但當局已對豬場展開刑事調查，警方在涉事豬場內發現約550隻豬被不人道對待，滿身糞便及受傷，「牠們明顯生病、十分痛苦」。當局已控告豬場虐待動物，罰款6,200歐元（5.1萬港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"9eecb6a6562dda2560e79eaa53705722b067923d","tid":91824,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e322fa64fc4e123fe090357386704f6eadde9e","tid":91824,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n<br />\n所有動物根本一生出來就係比人類食，有咩人道唔人道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ae163e18a77cd8df54ffe5758335a42cf90186","tid":91824,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"正式宣布 世界大戰現在開始！"},{"pid":"c93839b8a34e0435c9958ac63ddf9ad6d2393ec7","tid":91824,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"呢d豬就係港豬。死左投胎做意國豬。 抵死"},{"pid":"2945f4be565a90aa8e4ae494e6a656ade94b7b16","tid":91824,"uid":44948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"罰咁撚少錢, 起碼加多個零先有阻嚇作用"},{"pid":"d20df7b117b6c321d0b1ceed76f270576035af2d","tid":91824,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"5.1萬港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aebda53b340edda1f347b8e423416b04ff39709","tid":91824,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"佢地生存嘅價值就係成為食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地會對食材產生感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5ede95aea060520f0a1871c0723a338f3fb0f3","tid":91824,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bec78f0c84ecb1a100de409b8cd8ed2d025b1d5","tid":91824,"uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地生存嘅價值就係成為食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地會對食材產生感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會，會感謝佢既犧牲，所以食野通常清枱"},{"pid":"4172b0092c0d966dd904bf1bf6588cfc04ea47d2","tid":9182